    • Method Detail

      • getCorrectness

        Correctness getCorrectness()
        Returns the correctness of the query result.
        • If Correctness.SOUND_AND_COMPLETE, the query results are guaranteed to be correct.
        • If Correctness.SOUND_BUT_INCOMPLETE, the results are guaranteed to be sound, but may be incomplete.
        • If Correctness.INCORRECT, the results may be incomplete, and some results may be unsound.
        Returns:
        query result correctness
